<para style="q1">

<verse number="4" style="v" />Sing praises to Yahweh, you his faithful people! Give thanks when you remember his holiness.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="5" style="v" />For his anger is only for a moment; but his favor is for a lifetime.</para>

<para style="q1">Weeping comes for a night, but joy comes in the morning.</para>
